\newline 

\layout Standard

First, unpack the tarball:
\layout Standard


\family typewriter 
\size footnotesize 
$ tar -xzf php-4.0.6.tar.gz
\family default 
\size default 

\newline 

\layout Standard

Now, enter the source directory
\layout Standard


\family typewriter 
\size footnotesize 
$ cd php-4.0.6
\family default 
\size default 

\newline 

\layout Standard

Apply the kerberos workaround if necessary (se chapter 
